<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica;">We are planning to do a few activities around the date of the wedding, and also a trip after the wedding down to Phuket and Phi Phi islands, if anyone is interested. I've added a bunch of information and details to the invitation website at the link above. If you are interested in joining us, please update the&nbsp;box on the RSVP and let us know.</span></p>
